---------------
Jennic Demo Kit
---------------

This is the code provided with Jennic Demo Kit (Home Sensor Application). I
simply put them together with a makefile to enable compilation on Linux. Check
out the makefile to identify the expected path for ba2 toolchain.

--------
Building
--------

1. Run 'make base @ rotr @ node' (coordinator/router/end_device)
2. Edit location 0x30 - put in a valid 8-byte MAC address
3. Use my1jenflash to program JN5148 devices...
